videos.description: Matt Linehan connects with Kaden Elliss for the 7-yard touchdown pass to give the Vandals an early lead.
videos.headline: Idaho capitalizes on INT with TD pass

videos.description: Drew Lock comes back from interception and throws to Albert Okwuegbunam for the 19-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Mizzou answers quickly with TD pass of their own

videos.description: Richaud Floyd grabs the bouncing punt and doesn't look back, going 58 yards weaving through players for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Fancy footwork leads to Mizzou punt return TD

videos.description: Drew Lock quickly has two touchdowns on the afternoon. His second touchdown goes for 15 yards to J'Mon Moore.
videos.headline: Laser throw from Lock goes for TD

videos.description: Mizzou's offense is firing on all cylinders now with another touchdown pass to Albert Okwuegbunam.
videos.headline: Drew Lock notches 3rd TD pass

videos.description: Drew Lock and Albert Okwuegbunam are the dynamic duo connecting for the third time for a touchdown in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Lock has 4 TD passes in 1st quarter

videos.description: Matt Linehan passes to the back of the end zone to David Ungerer who comes down with the 8-yard touchdown catch.
videos.headline: Vandals add 2nd pass TD

videos.description: Ish Witter bounces to the outside and walks in for the 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Mizzou finds the end zone from the ground

videos.description: Drew Lock throws a dime in the end zone to a diving Emanuel Hall for the 20-yard score.
videos.headline: Lock ends first half with 5th TD pass

videos.description: Mizzou head coach Barry Odom is proud of the offensive firepower, but also likes the way the D-line is pressuring Idaho.
videos.headline: Coach Odom is impressed with the first half

videos.description: Ish Witter steamrolls up the middle for a 3-yard score.
videos.headline: Witter punches in 2nd rushing TD

videos.description: Have a day Drew Lock! This pass to Richaud Floyd is Lock's 6th touchdown pass of the game.
videos.headline: Lock tosses his 6th TD pass

videos.description: Mason Petrino comes in and throws a nice touchdown pass in a tight window to David Ungerer in the back of the end zone.
videos.headline: Idaho head coach's son throws TD pass

videos.description: Mizzou head coach Barry Odom tipped his hat to the performance of Drew Lock, but says the game was won on both sides of the ball.
videos.headline: Coach Odom pleased with team's performance

videos.description: Mizzou QB Drew Lock said the whole offense was clicking in the first half and that the Tigers look forward to the second half of the season.
videos.headline: Drew Lock talks about his 6 TD performance

videos.description: Mizzou was lead by Drew Lock's 6 touchdown passes in an all-around dominant effort against Idaho.
videos.headline: Missouri puts up a huge performance against Idaho
